♪The path of a hero may not work♪

64
00:02:59,990 --> 00:03:01,310
♪But we'll make our own way♪

65
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:02,860
=Hidden Master=

66
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:06,820
=Episode 21=

67
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:14,590
Yingdan?

68
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:16,310
Why are you here?

69
00:03:22,980 --> 00:03:25,180
(Sky Knight, He Changzai)

70
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:26,430
Master! Master!

71
00:03:26,430 --> 00:03:28,120
- What now?
- What do we do?

72
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,200
We've got this.

73
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:35,960
Vice Chairman He!

74
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,800
Vice Chairman!

75
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:37,870
Here you are.

76
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:41,520
What's the meaning of this?

77
00:03:43,710 --> 00:03:45,080
- We just want to see you.
- Yes, yes!

78
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,630
Liu's walnut crisps,

79
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:47,960
Zhou's sweet osmanthus brew,

80
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,150
and your favorite

81
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,150
Zhu's Nu'er Hong liquor.

82
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:55,310
- We've offended you before.
- Yes, truly.

83
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:57,240
We always made you angry.

84
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,120
That's right.

85
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,150
But you, sir,

86
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,630
you never held it against us.

87
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:02,870
Although you tricked me out of
my money,

88
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:03,800
this is...

89
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,640
Lingfeng!

90
00:04:05,310 --> 00:04:06,630
That wasn't tricking you out of money.

91
00:04:06,630 --> 00:04:09,080
That was contributing to the MAA's
daily needs!

92
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:11,430
Yes, yes! A contribution!

93
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,400
A noble cause!

94
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,910
What is the matter?

95
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:15,750
A small one.

96
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:16,920
A small one.

97
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:20,520
We want to ask Anicca Knight
something important.

98
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,680
But he's in jail right now.

99
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:23,870
Would you

100
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,710
be able to arrange a visit?

101
00:04:25,710 --> 00:04:27,680
- Anicca Knight?
- Yes.

102
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,520
A prison visit?

103
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,480
You know Anicca Knight

104
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,600
is now classified

105
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,950
as a top-level criminal.

106
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:35,870
Of course, of course.

107
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:38,830
He's being held jointly
by the authorities and MAA.

108
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,750
Yes, yes.

109
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:41,270
I don't have a problem with it,

110
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,560
right?

111
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,960
But

112
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:46,480
as for Inspector Deng,

113
00:04:47,630 --> 00:04:49,480
I'm afraid I can't help.

114
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:51,360
Deng Yunfeng?

115
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,510
I'll go talk to him.

116
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:58,560
You can give this to Inspector Deng.

117
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:01,160
This He Changzai

118
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,720
is so cunning!

119
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,190
Help!

120
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,120
Help!

121
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,270
Please save my son!

122
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:09,560
What's going on, sir?

123
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,560
My son

124
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:18,240
fell ill with a strange disease
last year.

125
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,120
We went to so many doctors,

126
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,360
- What happened?
- no one could cure him.

127
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:26,560
But this morning,

128
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,430
he suddenly

129
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,680
recovered,

130
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:35,160
said he wanted to come sell goods
with me.

131
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,600
I thought maybe

132
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,750
a deity had descended

133
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,510
and cured him.

134
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,830
We had just set up the stall,

135
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:46,000
and then, he collapsed.

136
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,390
Has your son ever seen Anicca Knight?

137
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:53,160
That Miracle Healer?

138
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,480
He's the greatest benefactor

139
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,310
of our family!

140
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:01,600
Son!

141
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,080
Deng Yunfeng,

142
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:05,950
Anicca Knight isn't the killer.

143
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:06,870
What nonsense.

144
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:09,240
He's a murderer, we caught him

145
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,240
red-handed.

146
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,000
There was an eighth murder just now.

147
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,800
But Anicca Knight is still locked up.

148
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,480
He couldn't possibly have done it.

149
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:16,710
Besides,

150
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,950
the victims

151
00:06:17,950 --> 00:06:20,240
all saw him as a lifesaver.

152
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,480
He wouldn't be the killer.

153
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,800
What are you doing?

154
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,310
If you don't believe it, come with me.

155
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:29,040
Stop pulling me around!

156
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,480
Those victims

157
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,600
were deceived by him.

158
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,160
Which means Anicca Knight

159
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,190
is even more cunning and

160
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:36,430
dangerous than we thought.

161
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,920
Deng Yunfeng!

162
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,000
Are you even being reasonable?

163
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,040
I follow evidence.

164
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:44,680
Why do you care so much
about Anicca Knight?

165
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,430
- I...
- Speak!

166
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:50,680
Yingdan is missing.

167
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:53,560
The last person she saw
was Anicca Knight.

168
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:57,630
At least let me see him once.

169
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,830
I want to know where she is.

170
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:00,950
What's that got to do with me?

171
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:02,240
I'm just in charge of the case.

172
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:04,710
- Deng Yunfeng!
- He's not here!

173
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:28,680
Where's my comb?

174
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:33,230
Sir!

175
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,680
Sir!

176
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,750
Master, be quick!

177
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,270
Sir!

178
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:45,040
Sir!

179
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,240
Can you please tell me
where Yingdan went?

180
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,750
You again?

181
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,840
Come closer.

182
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,920
I won't tell you.

183
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,070
Old man, don't push it too far!

184
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,270
Sir,

185
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:09,920
let's talk this out.

186
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,510
Don't be so stubborn, yeah?

187
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,120
I know you're not the killer.

188
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,390
And how do you know that?

189
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:20,190
Today, in Huizhou, a vendor's son died.

190
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:22,070
Same cause of death as the others.

191
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,430
Ah, that kid, huh?

192
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,320
That's right.

193
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,680
I really didn't kill anyone.

194
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:34,390
But their deaths are related to me.

195
00:08:34,830 --> 00:08:36,040
Related to you?

196
00:08:36,390 --> 00:08:37,600
What exactly did you do?

197
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,440
Yeah.

198
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,750
They took pills I gave them.

199
00:08:41,070 --> 00:08:42,670
But they weren't poison.

200
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,030
Not poison?

201
00:08:44,270 --> 00:08:45,440
Then how did they die?

202
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,270
It's a kind

203
00:08:47,630 --> 00:08:49,790
of medicine that dulls pain,

204
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,870
not lethal by itself.

205
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,910
But it speeds up the depletion

206
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:55,750
of a sick person's remaining energy.

207
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,960
It's like drinking poison
to quench thirst!

208
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,270
That is killing them!

209
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,480
You're a healer,

210
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:06,510
your job is to save lives!

211
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:08,790
People even call you the Anicca Knight!

212
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:11,030
You don't deserve the word "knight"!

213
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:12,120
Watch your mouth!

214
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,080
I don't deserve it?

215
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,000
Then who does?

216
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,720
Do you understand what it's like
to endure chronic pain?

217
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,870
Do you understand the torment
of waiting to die?

218
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:22,750
You don't.

219
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:25,150
I was helping them find peace.

220
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:34,550
Come on.

221
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,030
Sir!

222
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:40,230
Yingdan,

223
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:41,630
where did she go?

224
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:43,440
Enough already.

225
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,870
Sir.

226
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,600
Kid.

227
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:51,000
Gui Lao is your master, right?

228
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,440
How do you know that?

229
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,270
You knew my master?

230
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:58,550
Your master and I are old friends.

231
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,120
Righteousness and evil don't mix.

232
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:02,080
How could someone from the MAA

233
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,000
be friends with him?

234
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:07,480
Tell me,

235
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:10,550
what is righteousness? What is evil?

236
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,840
Saving lives is righteous.

237
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,840
Taking lives is evil.

238
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,840
You sure seem evil to me!

239
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:21,360
Few days back,

240
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,630
he came to Huizhou

241
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:24,910
bragging about his new disciple.

242
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,030
Said everything was great,

243
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,120
except the fierce-looking face.

244
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:31,720
When I checked your pulse recently,

245
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,120
I felt a strong inner power,

246
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,000
just like that old rascal.

247
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:37,360
And you really don't look like
a good guy.

248
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,720
Come on, sir,

249
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,270
back to the point, please!

250
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,320
Where is that old rascal now?

251
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:46,320
My master's dead.

252
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,840
Dead?

253
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:01,870
Where's he

254
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,510
buried?

255
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,630
At Wulipo,

256
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,870
south of Huizhou.

257
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:09,390
I set up a cenotaph for him.

258
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:14,390
Sir,

259
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:16,440
what are you doing?

260
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:19,550
This comb looks familiar.

261
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:20,550
I'm breaking out.

262
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:21,480
Breaking out?

263
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:25,750
I've known him a long time.

264
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,870
I have to go see him.

265
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,670
I heard noise, let's check it out.

266
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,200
People are coming, let's go!

267
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,120
Sir! Tell me

268
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,320
where Yingdan went!

269
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,510
Take care of yourself.

270
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:38,670
As for Miss Ma,

271
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:40,000
her fate is in her own hands.

272
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:42,150
- Just tell me!
- Go, go, go!

273
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,510
You've gone too far!

274
00:11:55,670 --> 00:11:56,670
Master.

275
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:58,080
Let's just leave.

276
00:11:58,190 --> 00:11:59,030
Let's go.

277
00:11:59,030 --> 00:11:59,960
That old man...

278
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,160
Wait a sec.

279
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:03,790
Have you gained weight lately?

