302
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,910
I'm not dreaming.

303
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,440
- Sorry.
- You really came back.

304
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,040
It's okay.

305
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:51,720
