306
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:53,270
Why's he here?

307
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:56,120
Lord Deng brought Yingdan back.

308
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,510
You've lost weight, I think.

309
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,030
Where have you been all these days?

310
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,320
I've been looking for you.

311
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,240
- These past few days I...
- Yingdan,

312
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:08,470
I'm gonna go first.

313
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,680
Okay.

314
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,480
Yunfeng,

315
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,600
