326
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,960
Don't treat Deng Yunfeng
like that again.

327
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,840
- He's a good person.
- He's not a good person!

328
00:13:44,030 --> 00:13:45,440
Yingdan, you don't know,

329
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,670
when I was looking for you,

330
