350
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,840
Sir,

351
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:47,960
you've suffered.

352
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:49,720
Oh, it's you.

353
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:51,800
No, no, don't.

354
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:53,320
