360
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,200
He promised I'd be his consort.

361
00:15:11,870 --> 00:15:13,360
Every day I lived,

362
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,750
I hoped

363
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,790
to enter the palace and marry him.

364
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,630
But

365
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:20,670
I got red butterfly rash,

366
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,240
an illness with no cure.

367
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,440
All I could do was wait to die,

368
00:15:24,270 --> 00:15:25,110
and

369
00:15:25,510 --> 00:15:28,150
