370
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,790
You saved me, sir.

371
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:32,800
Lord Deng,

372
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:35,320
I'm afraid I can't go with you

373
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:36,910
