that people died because of him.

398
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:07,440
Deng Yunfeng.

399
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,550
When did you get back?

400
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:09,630
Deng Yunfeng.

401
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:11,840
