407
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:27,510
This is the last mask, huh?

408
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:29,200
Heng, quit messing around!

409
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,510
I am really Ling'er!

410
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:31,640
What are you doing?

411
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:34,240
When I was talking to Yingdan just now,

412
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:35,110
she told me

