428
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:04,430
I did.

429
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:06,160
That's great!

430
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:08,030
My dear Yingdan's okay!

431
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:11,400
But let's be clear,

432
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:13,550
I still think Anicca Knight is a killer.

433
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:15,790
He's a physician,

434
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:17,240
