437
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:21,720
You're going to rescue him?

438
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:26,440
You don't have to come.

439
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:28,030
- I...
- Master,

440
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:29,680
can you not be so stubborn?

441
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:30,880
Anicca Knight didn't

442
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,590
decide who lives or dies.

443
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:34,720
When someone could be saved,

444
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:36,440
