445
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,160
I think Heng is right.

446
00:18:40,070 --> 00:18:40,920
Even so,

447
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,440
I still believe

448
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:44,030
