466
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:22,720
Don't worry.

467
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,390
Ling'er,

468
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:26,000
I'll protect you.

469
00:19:26,270 --> 00:19:27,200
Heng.

470
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,040
Good girl.

471
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:29,790
- Alright, let's go.
