00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,880
I'm starting to feel bad for Zhuge.

474
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,110
- So cute!
- Let's go!

475
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:38,950
Let's go.

476
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:43,750
