583
00:23:38,750 --> 00:23:41,590
The MAA recently solved
a serial murder case.

584
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,790
The Emperor has issued a decree

585
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,960
granting merit to us.

586
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,240
That merit

587
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,350
belongs to you.

588
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:52,400
I actually came here to talk to you
about that.

589
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:54,240
If I'm not mistaken,

590
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:56,350
it was you who freed Anicca Knight,
right?

591
00:23:56,350 --> 00:23:57,190
It was.

592
00:23:59,200 --> 00:24:01,270
But only after thorough investigation,
we realized

593
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:03,160
