601
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:17,960
There's no need for that.

602
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:19,960
But

603
00:24:20,590 --> 00:24:22,000
lately,

604
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,070
Eunuch Deng's influence

605
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:27,200
has been seeping into the MAA.

606
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:30,830
He deceives the court above

607
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:32,110
and bullies the people below.

608
00:24:36,790 --> 00:24:38,750
As Chairman of the MAA,

609
00:24:39,830 --> 00:24:42,310
I haven't been able to speak up
for the people

610
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:44,880
or bring peace to the martial world.

611
00:24:46,350 --> 00:24:47,200
It's laughable.

612
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:50,160
Without young people like you,

613
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:52,750
the MAA would be a complete joke.

614
00:24:54,830 --> 00:24:55,720
Gou Lingfeng,

615
00:24:57,790 --> 00:24:58,960
are you willing

616
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:01,310
to contribute more to the association?

617
00:25:01,310 --> 00:25:02,790
Uncle Wu, don't say that.

618
00:25:02,790 --> 00:25:03,920
I'd give my life if needed!

619
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,110
Then let me ask you:

620
00:25:05,350 --> 00:25:06,680
do you want to enter the Hero Gathering,

621
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:07,720
win the Hero Token,

622
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,110
and become my successor?

623
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:10,480
I do!

624
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:12,510
