the title—

641
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:43,200
Loyalty Knight.

642
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,000
Loyalty Knight!

643
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:47,480
That's my title now.

644
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:49,400
Loyalty Knight!

